content.html: PSA: Stop making developers feel like they HAVE to get involved in open source. You DO NOT HAVE TO participate in open source to A) be successful or B) give back to the community. You can be successful and give back to the community in MANY other ways.
content.value:
PSA: Stop making developers feel like they HAVE to get involved in open source. 

You DO NOT HAVE TO participate in open source to A) be successful or B) give back to the community.

You can be successful and give back to the community in MANY other ways.
